You might be at your final destination, but you are by no means happy about it.

00:02:33.127 --> 00:02:38.737
When you reach the enormous wooden doors, you are met not by servants, as you expected,

00:02:38.967 --> 00:02:46.917
but one single old man who introduces himself as Count Dracula and invites you inside.

00:02:48.047 --> 00:02:50.197
He speaks with a strong accent.

